Dialogue Text: I was trying to use my compass to find my cousin Delphia but it somehow malfunctioned midway...
Perhaps we might be near where she is.
Maybe she might be somewhere else.
I doubt so... This compass would let me know if I'm near her.
But I do recall of a place that might fix this compass. It's a unique house with two colours and no window panes.
Ah now that you mentioned it, I have an idea of where she might be!
Delphia loved that walnut-painted house we'd used to visit together in the past.
let's try to figure which building it is.
Let's try the brown colored house.
